vernac_cmds: Require Import ZArith NArith Nnat Ndec Ndigits.
Variable gc : BDDconfig -> list ad -> BDDconfig.

Fixpoint BDDuniv_1 (cfg : BDDconfig) (ul : list ad) (node : ad) (y : BDDvar) (bound : nat) {struct bound} : BDDconfig * ad := match bound with | O => (initBDDconfig, BDDzero) | S bound' => match MapGet2 _ (um_of_cfg cfg) node y with | Some node' => (cfg, node') | None => match MapGet _ (fst cfg) node with | None => (cfg, node) | Some (x, (l, r)) => match BDDcompare x y with | Datatypes.Lt => (cfg, node) | Datatypes.Eq => BDDand gc cfg ul l r | Datatypes.Gt => match BDDuniv_1 cfg ul l y bound' with | (cfgl, nodel) => match BDDuniv_1 cfgl (nodel :: ul) r y bound' with | (cfgr, noder) => match BDDmake gc cfgr x nodel noder (noder :: nodel :: ul) with | (cfg', node') => (BDDuniv_memo_put cfg' y node node', node') end end end end end end end.

Lemma BDDuniv_1_lemma : forall (bound : nat) (cfg : BDDconfig) (ul : list ad) (u : BDDvar) (node : ad), nat_of_N (node_height cfg node) < bound -> BDDconfig_OK cfg -> used_list_OK cfg ul -> used_node' cfg ul node -> BDDconfig_OK (fst (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) /\ config_node_OK (fst (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) (snd (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) /\ used_nodes_preserved cfg (fst (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) ul /\ Nleb (node_height (fst (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) (snd (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound))) (node_height cfg node) = true /\ bool_fun_eq (bool_fun_of_BDD (fst (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound)) (snd (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul node u bound))) (bool_fun_forall u (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg node)).
elim y; clear y; intros node' H4.
elim (um_of_cfg_OK _ H1 u node node' H4).
intro x; elim x; clear x; intros x x0; elim x0; clear x0; intros l r H4.
apply Nleb_trans with (b := BDDvar_max (node_height cfg l) (node_height cfg r)).
apply lt_le_trans with (m := max (nat_of_N (node_height cfg node)) (nat_of_N (node_height cfg node))).
apply bool_fun_eq_trans with (bf2 := bool_fun_forall u (bool_fun_if x (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg r) (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg l))).
apply bool_fun_eq_trans with (bf2 := bool_fun_and (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg r) (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg l)).
apply bool_fun_eq_trans with (bf2 := bool_fun_and (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg l) (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg r)).
apply BDDvar_independent_high with (x := x) (l := l) (node := node).
apply BDDvar_independent_low with (x := x) (r := r) (node := node).
elim (prod_sum _ _ (BDDuniv_1 cfg ul l u n)).
elim (prod_sum _ _ (BDDuniv_1 cfgl (nodel :: ul) r u n)).
elim (prod_sum _ _ (BDDmake gc cfgr x nodel noder (noder :: nodel :: ul))).

cut (BDDconfig_OK cfgl /\ config_node_OK cfgl nodel /\ used_nodes_preserved cfg cfgl ul /\ Nleb (node_height cfgl nodel) (node_height cfg l) = true /\ bool_fun_eq (bool_fun_of_BDD cfgl nodel) (bool_fun_forall u (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg l))).

cut (BDDconfig_OK cfgr /\ config_node_OK cfgr noder /\ used_nodes_preserved cfgl cfgr (nodel :: ul) /\ Nleb (node_height cfgr noder) (node_height cfgl r) = true /\ bool_fun_eq (bool_fun_of_BDD cfgr noder) (bool_fun_forall u (bool_fun_of_BDD cfgl r))).
cut (forall (xl : BDDvar) (ll rl : ad), MapGet _ (fst cfgr) nodel = Some (xl, (ll, rl)) -> BDDcompare xl x = Datatypes.Lt).
cut (forall (xr : BDDvar) (lr rr : ad), MapGet _ (fst cfgr) noder = Some (xr, (lr, rr)) -> BDDcompare xr x = Datatypes.Lt).
cut (bool_fun_eq (bool_fun_of_BDD cfg' node') (bool_fun_if x (bool_fun_of_BDD cfgr noder) (bool_fun_of_BDD cfgr nodel))).
cut (nodes_preserved cfg' (BDDuniv_memo_put cfg' u node node')).
rewrite (Neqb_complete (node_height (BDDuniv_memo_put cfg' u node node') node') (node_height cfg' node')).
apply bool_fun_eq_trans with (bf2 := bool_fun_of_BDD cfg' node').
